@Node Requirements "Requirements"

  @{B}@{U}Requirements@{UU}@{UB}
  
  Hardware :
  
  · An Amiga (ECS and above)
   
  Software :
  
  · MUI 3.8+
  · locale.library 38+
  · These commands in the path (e.g. c:) :
    - AddBuffers
    - Copy
    - Dir
    - Execute
    - MakeDir
    - Mount
    - Rename
  · A Doom engine and at least one doom wad file
  
@EndNode
@Node Installation "Installation"

  @{B}@{U}Installation@{UU}@{UB}
  
  Just copy the executable where you want! If you want to install a
catalog, copy it into LOCALE:Catalogs/language/
where language is a language (e.g. français).

  If someone wants to make an Installer script to install it, he can
send us it :)

@EndNode
@Node Using "Using"

  @{B}@{U}Using@{UU}@{UB}

  There shouldn't be any problem. Just don't forget to correctly set
the paths, and it should work.

@EndNode
